{panel:title=What do you like?|borderColor=#ccc| titleBGColor=#c2ffa2|bgColor=#fff}
For clarity, I often do multiple PRs for a single fix. I would like to have an easy way of linking between PRs with Markdown. For example:
* #300 for PR 300 in the same repo,
* repoName#123 for cross-repo link,
* JIRA/someplugin#500 for cross-project.
{panel}

